Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:04.47,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I don't like this system at all.}Mình vẫn không phục.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:09.13,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Doesn't making us clean up when \Nthe date matches our student number}Tự nhiên bắt dọn dẹp khi số thứ tự trùng với ngày dọn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:11.15,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{let students in the 30s off the hook?}Nó có khiến chúng ta bớt khó khăn hơn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:17.11,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Y-Yakishio-san?}Y-Yakishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.99,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hey, Nukumizu.}Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.95,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I need to talk to you about something.}Tớ có chuyện muốn nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Normally, this sort of thing foreshadows\N a very arousing turn of events.}Bình thường sẽ tiến triển đến thứ thú vị đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.46,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But in rom-com terms, \NYakishio and I are short on plot developments}Trong cốt truyện romcom thì mình\N và Yakishio sẽ phát triển quan hệ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.94,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{that would lead to an incident \Nin the gym storage room.}dựa vào sự kiện tai nạn tại nhà kho này!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.83,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{So what happened with that thing?}Nè, chuyện đó sao rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.80,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? What "thing" do you mean?}Chuyện đó là gì...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.94,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Oh, you know.}Thì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:54.65,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Mitsuki said he was gonna borrow books \Nfrom the lit club. Did he do that already?}Mitsuki nói sẽ đến mượn sách\N ở CLB ấy. Cậu ấy mượn chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.40,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, that "thing."}À chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:02.73,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I-If it's okay, I wouldn't mind \Ntaking the books to him myself.}T-Tớ muốn đưa nó cho cậu ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.28,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Okay, how about this:}À vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:14.47,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Why don't we get him to pick them up\Nwhen you have a day off from your club?}Sao không kêu cậu ta đến lấy sách lúc cậu nghỉ CLB?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.22,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{My club? Why?}CLB của tớ á? Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:21.77,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, because it'd probably be okay\N for you to visit the lit club then.}Vì thỉnh thoảng cậu đến CLB văn học,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.89,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{As an observer or whatever.}để quan sát hay đọc sách gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:27.46,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{An observer? Me?}Tớ? Đọc sách á?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:32.81,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I mean, you could even \Ncome to the club together then.}Ừ, nếu thế thì sẽ có cớ đi cùng cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.02,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Both of you. Together.}Hai người. Đi cùng nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.96,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Of course! Nukumizu, you're really smart!}Ra là vậy! Nukumizu, cậu thông minh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.20,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You're actually not such a bad guy.\N I had you all wrong.}Tính ra cũng tốt tính. Tớ hiểu lầm cậu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.81,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I think the entire class has me all wrong.}Không lẽ cả cái lớp này ai cũng hiểu lầm mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:50.41,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Uh-oh.}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.46,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.87,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{It looks like...}Có vẻ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:57.15,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{the door might be locked from outside.}cửa bị khoá rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:57.96,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.96,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.01,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.01,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Somebody help!}Có ai không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.13,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{We're still in here!}Bọn tôi vẫn còn ở trong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.13,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:11.61,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{The forecast said the temperature \Nwas gonna get up to 35 degrees today.}Theo dự báo thì nhiệt độ là 35 độ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.74,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's the first really hot day of the summer.}Là ngày nóng nhất mùa hè...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.18,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Whoa. She must have a super fast metabolism.}Cậu ta trao đổi chất nhanh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.35,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey, Yakishio-san, you okay?}Nè Yakishio, ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:27.94,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I'm fine. I'm more like an impala\Nthan a Thomson's gazelle.}Ổn ổn. Tớ giống linh dương\N hơn là linh dương Thomson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.90,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Really? You're an impala?}Cậu là linh dương à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.92,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Basically, it's a lot faster to run on four legs.}Thế nên chạy bằng 4 chân sẽ nhanh hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:41.63,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{What I'm saying is, spotted hyenas \Nlike to get splashed with water!}Những con linh cẩu thích bị tạt nước lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.36,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{She definitely doesn't sound okay!}Ổn cái gì mà ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.63,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yakishio-san, here! It's a cooling spray!}Yakishio, chai xịt lạnh nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.27,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Ooh, Nuk-kun, nice one!}Ồ, Nuk-kun, tuyệt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.89,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Am I "Nuk-kun" now?}Giờ mình thành Nuk-kun à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.47,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Spray it all over me.}Mau bắn lên người tớ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.27,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Ah! Wait a second!}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.17,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hurry up.}Nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.17,0:05:03.65,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I never thought the day would come \Nwhen a girl was begging for me!}Không ngờ cái ngày gái cầu xin\N mình bắn lên lại diễn ra.
