Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.71,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{600 yen! Thank you very much!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:35.17,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Sounds like you guys are having fun.}Mấy cậu có vẻ vui nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:39.18,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, Lemon-chan! Good morning. \NAre you feeling better?}Lemon-chan, chào cậu. Khoẻ lại chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.98,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Much, much better.}Ừm, khoẻ như trâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:45.18,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{But I don't remember what happened \Nat the end. How did we end up?}Nhưng chẳng nhớ gì cả. Có chuyện gì xảy ra nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? Um, no, uh...}Hả? À không...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.88,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{A-Amanatsu-sensei rescued us.}Cô Amanatsu đã cứu chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:50.93,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.39,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Then I guess Amanatsu-sensei \Nchanged my clothes for me.}Vậy là cô ấy thay đồ hộ tớ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:56.84,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Right! Amanatsu-sensei \Nchanged your clothes.}Phải! Cô ấy đã thay đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.20,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{And I didn't see a thing. Not a thing.}Và tớ không nhìn thấy gì đâu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.03,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You'd better not have. What sort\Nof creep watches a girl changing?}Còn phải hỏi à?\N Con trai mà nhìn con gái thay đồ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.01,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu-kun, that's kinda gross.}Nukumizu, gớm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.81,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Don't say that. \NI won't be able to face another day.}Đừng có nói câu đó với bộ mặt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:11.28,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{But anyway, what's that? It looks delicious.}Cơ mà gì kia? Ngon vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.60,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I know, right? I made it myself.}Tớ tự làm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.18,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Here. Say "ahh."}Nè, Aaaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.88,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Why is she feeding her from my plate?}Mắc gì lấy từ dĩa của mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.85,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Wow, yum! What is this sauce? It's so wild!}Ngon quá! Sốt gì vậy? Đỉnh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.30,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{Why, it's from the Empire Hotel!}Dĩ nhiên, từ khách sạn Empire đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.50,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Uh, that's actually my lunch.}Đó là... bữa trưa của tớ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.87,Top,Lemon,0,0,0,,{The Empire Hotel?!}Khách sạn Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.32,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Nuk-kun?}Sao thế Nuk-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:33.17,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah. I guess that counts\N as an indirect kiss.}Cậu nghĩ đó là hôn gián tiếp nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.39,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Mind out of the gutter, son. You're at school.}Hãy vượt qua nó đi, chàng trai. Đang ở trường đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:36.99,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I wasn't thinking anything dirty!}Tớ không có nghĩ thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.64,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? Then why are you blushing?}Vậy sao lại xấu hổ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.18,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I-I'm not!}K-Không có!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.36,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Excuse me. Is Lemon here?}Xin lỗi, Lemon có ở đây không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.62,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,M-Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:48.50,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Are you feeling better? Here. \NI brought you a get-well gift.}Cậu ổn chưa? Nè, tớ mang ít đồ cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.05,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You brought this for me?}Cậu mua nó cho tớ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.99,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{But you seem fine. Maybe you don't need it.}Cơ mà trông cậu có vẻ\N khoẻ nên chắc không cần nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:57.36,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I do! I was feeling so bad, \NI couldn't eat at all!}Không không! Tớ mệt tới nỗi không ăn nổi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.22,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Yeah, sure looks like it.}À ừm, có vẻ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.79,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{You can't eat it if it's on your cheek.}Không ăn mà dính cơm trên mặt nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.97,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Um, thank you.}Cảm ơn cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.52,Default,Chihaya,0,0,0,,{Mitsuki-san!}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.70,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Oh, Chihaya. What's up?}Chihaya, sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:15.52,Default,Chihaya,0,0,0,,{I was thinking of going to the study room \Nafter class. Would you like to join me?}Tớ nghĩ đến phòng tự học \Nsau giờ học. Cậu có đi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.99,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry. Gotta go home early today. \NI'll see you at cram school tomorrow.}Xin lỗi, hôm nay tớ phải về sớm. \NMai gặp ở lớp học thêm nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:23.97,Default,Chihaya,0,0,0,,{Got it. Then I'll get in touch later tonight.}Hiểu rồi. Vậy tối nay tớ lại gọi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.75,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Silly. I said I'll see you tomorrow.}Thiệt tình, đã nói mai gặp rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.09,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{I'd better get back to class. \NLemon, take it easy, okay?}Vậy tớ quay lại lớp đây. Đừng cố quá nhé Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.04,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{S-Sure. Thanks.}À ừm. Cảm ơn.
