Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.01,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Nuk-kun, good morning!}Nuk-kun, chào buổi sáng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.45,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{O-Oh, g-good morning.}À ừm, chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.85,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Listen, I finally remembered what happened\N in the storage room yesterday.}À, tớ nhớ ra chuyện xảy ra ở kho rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.12,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{So today, after class—}Thế nên là sau giờ học--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.85,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Ah! Y-You remembered what happened?}C-Cậu nhớ ra rồi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.27,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Nope! I didn't see! \NI didn't see anything at all!}Tớ không thấy gì hết! Thề!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:04.66,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{What? We talked about me going \Nto the lit club with Mitsuki today.}Chuyện gì? Đang nói vụ\N đi cùng Mitsuki đến CLB văn học.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.24,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:09.86,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Didn't you say we should come together? \NDid the heat fry your brain, too?}Cậu nói hai người nên đi \Ncùng nhau đó. Nóng quá hoá rồ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.97,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's right. Yeah, I totally did.}À à, chuyện đó nhỉ. Chắc chắn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.70,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yup, yup. Sounds good.}Ừm, ừm. Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.54,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Okay, see you after class.}Vậy gặp sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.96,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Lemon-chan sure is going after him.}Lemon đang rất cố gắng nhỉ.
