Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.81,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Th-That sci-fi book I borrowed \Nwas really good.}C-Cuốn sách anh cho em mượn thú vị lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.88,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I didn't really get it, but—}Tuy vẫn chưa hiểu hết nhưng--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.18,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{You thought so?}Thật à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.58,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Ah, I knew you had good taste, Komari-chan.}Em đúng là có khẩu vị tinh tế đấy, Komari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.47,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Whoa there.}Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.05,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Komari-chan, if you don't like that,\N I'll tell him off myself.}Komari, nếu không thích em có thể nói mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.33,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I...}E-Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.15,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{My head... d-doesn't really... uh, hate it.}Đầu em... không hẳn là... không thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.70,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,Đúng là dễ thương mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.01,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{You should learn from her example, Koto.}Cậu cũng nên học em ấy đi, Koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.00,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Shaddap.}Im đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.41,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{See you later.}Vậy gặp sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:43.93,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{The p-president... He called... \NHe called me a c-cutie.}H-Hội trưởng gọi mình dễ thương...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.17,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{You two sure get along well.}Hai người thân thiết nhau ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.63,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Well, we're childhood friends. \NWe're kinda stuck together.}Ừm, bạn thuở nhỏ mà. \NDính với nhau như lời nguyền luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.91,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Childhood friends?}Bạn thuở nhỏ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.35,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{That must mean...}Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.31,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Homewrecker.}Thứ trà xanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:04.15,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{C-Cmon, Yanami-san.\NLet's not use that talk in here.}Này Yanami, đừng nói thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:04.90,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um—}À--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.11,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Excuse us.}Xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.69,Top,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Lemon, behave yourself, okay?}Lemon, cẩn thận đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:11.08,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Ayano. Nice timing.}Ayano, may quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:17.66,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{This really is an outstanding collection.\N Which one should I borrow?}Nhìn đỉnh thật. Nên mượn cuốn nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.63,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Take whatever you like.}Cứ lấy thoải mái đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:24.68,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{But if you decide to join our club, you'll be \Nable to borrow anything freely. Interested?}Nhưng nếu quyết định tham gia CLB \Nthì em sẽ được mượn miễn phí đó. Thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.54,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{I am interested, \Nbut I'm busy with cram school.}Em có hứng thú nhưng khá là bận học.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:32.76,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's no problem. You can come \Nand borrow books whenever you feel like it.}Không sao. Chỉ cần đến mượn sách là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.62,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{And maybe your cute \Ngirlfriend wants to join, too?}Và bạn gái dễ thương kia thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.92,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? What? M-Me?}Hả? E-Em á?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.17,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Do you mean me when you say "girlfriend"?}Bạn gái là em á?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:45.52,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Oh, gosh! But I'm in the track club,\N so that might be difficult.}Nhưng em trong CLB điền kinh nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.92,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Tsk, tsk, tsk. We're totally open\N to dual memberships.}Không sao, CLB của bọn chị chấp nhận tham gia 2 CLB.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.48,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{I mean, all of our members \Nare in other clubs, too.}Cơ mà thành viên trong này toàn 2 CLB không đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:55.03,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Seriously? What other club am I in?}Thật à? Mình có tham gia CLB khác nữa hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:59.19,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{You can come hide here if you \Never want to skip track practice.}Em có thể đến đây mỗi khi muốn trốn điền kinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:03.23,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Right? And wouldn't it be nice to have \Nmore time to spend with your girlfriend?}Và em cũng có nhiều thời gian với bạn gái nữa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.53,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? Would you like that, Mitsuki?}Hả? Cậu thấy vui hả, Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.97,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{That wouldn't be fair to Lemon. \NWe aren't dating, anyway.}Không phải đâu. Bọn em có hẹn hò đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.31,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Oh? You're not?}Không phải hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:16.30,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{She's always been really popular with \Nthe guys. I wouldn't stand a chance.}Cậu ta từ xưa đã nổi tiếng với đám\N con trai rồi. Em làm gì có cửa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.84,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Anyway, thanks for letting me borrow—}Vậy cảm ơn vì đã cho em mượn sách--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.22,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{That's not true!}Không đúng!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:25.58,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I don't have a boyfriend, and being popular\n doesn't mean I'd go with just anyone!}Tớ không có bạn trai, \Nvà nổi tiếng không có nghĩa là dễ dãi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.19,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{O-Oh. Right.}V-Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.57,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Sorry, did I say something wrong?}Xin lỗi, tớ nói gì sai hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.54,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Not exactly, but...}Không hẳn nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:37.78,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Um, I... Sorry.}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.43,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Ôi chà!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:44.53,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Are you sure you two aren't dating? \NYou sure act like a couple.}Cả hai có chắc là không hẹn hò không vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.83,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{N-No, we don't!}Không có ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.54,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Huh. Are you sure?}Chắc chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.89,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{But we aren't!}Thật mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.38,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,Vâng, với cả em có bạn gái rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:18:00.26,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H30&\t(1200,1700,\alpha&HAB&)\t(1748,1749,\alpha&H35&)\t(2850,3250,\alpha&HAE&)\t(3289,3290,\alpha&H40&)\t(4000,4400,\alpha&HBA&)\t(4450,4451,\alpha&H50&)\t(5100,5400,\alpha&HCA&)\t(5460,5461,\alpha&H70&)\t(6000,6300,\alpha&HDA&)\t(6375,6376,\alpha&H90&)\t(7200,7500,\alpha&HFF&)}{I already have a girlfriend.}Em có bạn gái rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.72,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Huh? What?}Hả? Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.45,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, everyone?}Mọi người sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:10.46,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? Um, Mitsuki... You got a girlfriend?}Mitsuki... cậu có bạn gái rồi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:14.15,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Just recently. \NI guess I hadn't told you yet, Lemon.}À ừm, mới gần đây. Tớ chưa nói cho cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.03,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Let me guess. Is it Asagumo-san?}Để tớ đoán nhé, là Asagumo nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.45,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Was it that obvious?}Lộ rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:22.00,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Well, yeah. I'll introduce \Nyou guys properly next time.}Ừm, lần tới tớ sẽ giới thiệu cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.79,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{All right, Lemon. Wanna get going?}Vậy nhé, Lemon, đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.70,Default,Koto; Nukumizu; Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.16,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Didn't you want to go \Nshopping together today?}Cậu nói muốn đi mua sắm cùng nhau mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:31.63,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{No way. Is Ayano actually totally dense?}Tên Ayano này... bị ngu à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:36.80,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I-I've decided to join the lit club, \Nso I think I'll hang out here for a bit.}T-Tớ quyết định sẽ tham gia\N CLB văn học rồi nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.34,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Oh, okay. Then I guess I'll see you later.}Vậy à. Thế gặp sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.09,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Was that maybe... my fault?}Không lẽ... là tại chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yup, that was your fault.}Chính xác. Là tại chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.85,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? What is it?}Gì nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.75,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Gimme an application form.}Cho tớ đơn gia nhập CLB.
