Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.36,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh. So Mitsuki already had a girlfriend?}Mitsuki có bạn gái rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:03.64,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{What have I been doing all this time?}Tớ đã làm trò gì suốt thời gian qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:06.30,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Running in circles, I guess.}Chạy vòng tròn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:09.53,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Anyway, welcome. Wear this.}À thì... chào mừng thành viên mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.53,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I will. I'm all worn out.}Tớ mệt mỏi quá rồi.
