Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Your friend basically got dumped, \Nso to cheer her up,}Vì bạn mình bị thất tình, để an ủi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:26.26,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{you take her to the restaurant where }{\i0}{you}{\i1}{ \Ngot dumped? Do you have nerves of steel?!}nên dẫn đến cái nhà hàng \Ncậu ta từng bị đá hả? Thần kinh thép vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:31.36,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, uh, Yanami-san...\NYou're paying for yourself today, right?}Yanami này... hôm nay cậu tự trả tiền cho mình đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:35.98,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Of course! But talking about money in front \Nof a girl who just had her heart broken...}Dĩ nhiên rồi. Nhưng nói chuyện\N tiền bạc trước mặt gái có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.95,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Have you no tact at all?}Cậu không tế nhị gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:40.42,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Lemon-chan, we'll treat you today.}Lemon-chan, bọn tớ sẽ đãi cậu hôm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.49,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Um, you don't have to.}Không cần phải vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.62,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's okay.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.21,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{We're celebrating you joining the club, too.}Chúng ta ăn mừng cậu gia nhập CLB luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.66,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{All right, I'm gonna have a Hamburg steak!}Vậy tớ sẽ gọi hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:51.75,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yanami-san, are you okay \Neating that much before dinner?}Yanami, ăn trước bữa tối ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:56.25,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Didn't you know? \NSweets are a diet's worst enemy.}Không biết hả? Đồ ngọt là kẻ thù của ăn kiêng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.61,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{And a Hamburg steak\Nbefore dinner is a diet's ally?}Vậy ăn hamburger là đồng minh của ăn kiêng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:03.29,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{All right, I think I'll have\N a bean paste sundae.}Vậy thì tớ gọi sundae đậu đỏ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:05.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh my gosh! \NI think I'll have that for dessert.}Gì thế? Tớ cũng muốn thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.56,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I thought sweets were the enemy?}Sao nói đồ ngọt là kẻ thù?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.40,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Then I'll add a hamburger, too.}Vậy tớ sẽ gọi hamburger ăn kèm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.12,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Can you really eat that much?}Cậu ăn nhiều vậy được à?
